(1,	3,	2,	1,	'2011-12-02',	'<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><span>Project:<span> </span>Social Media</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<h3><span><span><span> </span></span></span><span>Activities this period</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Incorporated additional comments from the Stakeholder Engagement team into the New Media Strategy on 11/29/11. Incorporated Public Affairs comments and provided notes to AlTariq regarding comments on 11/29/11.<span> </span>Provide AlTariq with updated New Media Strategy for review on 11/29/11.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong>Project:<span> </span>SLM</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><span><span> </span>Activities this period</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Met with Fred & Sayed to discuss SLM feedback on 11/28/11.<span> </span>Sayed stated that Diane and Taqueer would also be reviewing it and providing feedback.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><span></span>Met with Fred & AlTariq to discuss SLM and CPIC alignment on 11/28/11.<span> </span>Sent information for clarification to AlTariq. </span><span><span>Per CPIC, the ITIB reviews a project to approve a Mission Needs Statement and when the Exhibit 300 information is complete. Exhibit 300/ITIB presentation requirements along with specific artifact requirements are only met after the planning of the project is complete. The process to get from the Mission Needs Statement to the Exhibit 300 is defined by the SLM. The SLM process provides completed deliverables to CPIC after the Planning and Requirements Phases are complete. Essentially 570 guides the process through these phases and then coordinates with 550/CPIC to provide their requested deliverables only after those phases are complete. </span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Met with AlTariq, Fred and Mr. Lewis on 11/30/11 to discuss SLM and guidance of projects.<span> </span>We all came to an agreement of what the process should incorporate and when the ITIB should be involved (Completion of Mission Needs Statement, Completion of Pre-Planning and Completion of Planning and Requirements).<span> </span>We were instructed by AlTariq to complete the IM and to notify the business that we are the point of contact for 500.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong>Project:<span> </span>Geospatial Publication Investment (aka Geospatial Communication Tool)</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><span><span> </span>Activities this period</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span>Left message with Beth on 11/28/11 in regards to status and scope definition. Discussed status with AlTariq.<span> </span>Discussed scope and responsibility of ITIB interpretation on 11/29/11 with Fred and AlTariq to ensure we were providing proper guidance.<span> </span>AlTariq stated that we do not interpret ITIB decisions and any business should ask their AD.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span>Discussed GPI in the previously noted SLM meeting.<span> </span>I provided Beth feedback to her request for status on 11/30/11.<span> </span>I also provided guidance for communications as directed by Ronnie.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span>Per the direction of Mr. Samuels, I proceeded with development of SLM artifacts for the business.<span> </span>I transferred information into the Project Management Plan and completed the information available to date on 12/1/11.<span> </span>I created a Change Management Plan and Communications Plan on 12/1/11.<span> </span>I created an Acquisitions Plan and Quality Management Plan on 12/2/11.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><span></span></span></span></p>',	'<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><em><span>Project:<span> </span>Social Media</span></em></strong></span></p>\r\n<h3><span><span></span></span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span><strong><span>Accomplishments</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\">Provided Al\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\'Tariq with updated New Media Strategy for review 11/29/11. He distributed it to teams.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span>Meetings and Presentations</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong><em>Project:<span> </span>SLM</em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span><strong><span>Accomplishments</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Worked with Fred to align artifacts to move forward with Geospatial Publication Investment<strong>.</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong><em>Project:<span> </span>Geospatial Publication Investment (aka Geospatial Communication Tool)</em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><em><span><span></span></span></em></strong></span><span><span><strong>Accomplishments</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<h3><span>Transferred information into the Project Management Plan and completed the information available to date on 12/1/11.<span> C</span>reated a Change Management Plan and Communications Plan on 12/1/11.<span> C</span>reated an Acquisitions Plan and Quality Management Plan on 12/2/11.</span></h3>',	'<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><em><span>Project:<span> </span>Social Media</span></em></strong></span></p>\r\n<h3><span><span><span></span></span></span><span>Meetings and Presentations</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span>Met with Al\\\\\\\'Tariq on 12/1/11 to discuss meeting with teams regarding revised strategy. Al\\\\\\\'Tariq sent out revised Strategy to teams with request for meeting.</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong><em></em><em></em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span><strong><em>Project:<span> </span>SLM</em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><strong><em><span><span></span></span></em></strong></span><strong><span>Meetings and Presentations</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Met with Fred & Sayed to discuss SLM feedback on 11/28/11.<span> Sayedis ok with the process because CPIC recieves requested deliverables but hehas been directed by Diane that Taqueer and herself must also review the document prior to giving official feedback.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Met with Fred & AlTariq to discuss SLM and CPIC alignment on 11/28/11. Al\\\\\\\'Tariq believes that it is a good process and understands that CPIC recieves their completed deliverables after Planning and Requirements are complete.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span><span>Met with AlTariq, Fred and Mr. Lewis on 11/30/11 to discuss SLM and guidance of projects.<span> Al\\\\\\\'Tariq requested that AFMSS and GPI be aligned in the SLM process at their current status.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\\"><span></span></p>',	'<p>n/a</p>',	'<p>n/a</p>\r\n<p></p>',	2,	4,	'2011-12-05 17:50:35',	3,	'2011-12-08 18:12:08'),
(2,	3,	2,	1,	'2011-12-09',	'<p><strong>Geospatial Publication Investment</strong></p>\r\n<p>Compiled information for the SLM Business Case document on 12/5/11.&nbsp; Prepared Risk Management Log and Change Mangement Log on 12/5/11.</p>\r\n<p>Worked with Fred on 12/6/11 to provide support to GPI in regards to the overall project planning.&nbsp; We discussed GPI\'s work breakdown flow and how we could&nbsp;help the team could better understand supporting technologies.</p>\r\n<p>Discussed GPI\'s status via phone with Beth on 12/6/11.&nbsp; She had several questions about the ITIB presentation in January.&nbsp; I requested clarification from Al\'Tariq via email.</p>\r\n<p>Al\'Tariq provided clarification on 12/7/11.&nbsp; He agree that the presentation would include the following items: Scope, High Level Requirements, Benefits, Outline of Alternatives, Cost for Planning, Items included in Planning.</p>\r\n<p>Worked with Fred&nbsp;to compile appropriate questions for the GPI team to&nbsp;evaluate in regards to integrating with the systems where they will be obtaining data from on 12/7/11. Provided&nbsp;Beth with&nbsp;integration quesitons and explanations on 12/8/11.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>SLM</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p>Discussed Project Charter template along with the status of the Geospatial Publication and AFMSS in regards to the SLM process with Mr. Lewis and Fred on 12/7/11.&nbsp; We are reviewing templates to ensure that they are tailored specifically to BLM\'s needs.</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>New Media/Social Media</strong></p>\r\n<p>Met with Al\'Tariq on 12/8/11 to discuss current version of strategy and information needed for the meeting on 12/8/11.&nbsp; Prepared a table listing team comments and revisions for review during the meeting.</p>\r\n<p>Reviewed strategy for alignment on 12/9/11.&nbsp; Reviewed additional comments from team leads regarding objective of the Strategy.&nbsp; Alexandra is preparing a Problem Statement.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Other</strong></p>\r\n<p>Per Al\'Tariq, I worked with Patrick to research information regarding bandwith estimates for offices.&nbsp; I contacted Jeremy Wilcox at Forrester for information.&nbsp; He provided feedback in an email.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>',	'<p><strong>Geospatial Publication Investment</strong></p>\r\n<p>Compiled information for the SLM Business Case document on 12/5/11.&nbsp; Prepared Risk Management Log and Change Mangement Log on 12/5/11.</p>\r\n<p>Discussed GPI\'s status via phone with Beth on 12/6/11 and requested&nbsp;clarification from Al\'Tariq via email.</p>\r\n<p>Came to an agreement that the ITIB&nbsp;presentation would include the following items: Scope, High Level Requirements, Benefits, Outline of Alternatives, Cost for Planning, Items included in Planning.</p>\r\n<p>Provided&nbsp;Beth with&nbsp;integration quesitons and explanations on 12/8/11.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>New Media/Social Media</strong></p>\r\n<p>Met with Al\'Tariq on 12/8/11 to discuss current version of strategy and information needed for the meeting on 12/8/11.&nbsp; Prepared a table listing team comments and revisions for review during the meeting.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Other</strong></p>\r\n<p>Per Al\'Tariq, I provided research information to Patrick for bandwith estimates.</p>',	'<p><strong>Geospatial Publication Investment</strong></p>\r\n<p>Met with Fred on 12/6/11 to discuss work breakdown flow of previous project and how it could relate to GPI.&nbsp; Fred revised presentation and we met with Dan O on 12/6/11 to discuss the work breakdown flow.&nbsp; Dan O. was very receptive and impressed.&nbsp; The main slide was sent to Beth for additional review.</p>\r\n<p><strong>New Media/Social Media</strong></p>\r\n<p>Met with Al\'Tariq and Team Leaders to discuss revisions to the New Media Strategy on 12/8/11. We discussed the strategy overall.&nbsp; Alexandra will prepare a problem statement.&nbsp; I will review the document to ensure that it aligns with business needs.&nbsp; Al\'Tariq also stated that team leads and myself can revise the \"Next Steps\" if we find it necessary.&nbsp; After the meeting, I reminded him that Ronnie had already approved the Next Steps.&nbsp; He stated that we could still request a revision even if she didnt accept it.</p>',	'<p>n/a</p>',	'<p>n/a</p>',	2,	4,	'2011-12-06 17:09:26',	3,	'2011-12-12 23:23:58'),
