(5,	6,	1,	1,	'2011-12-09',	'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Worked on completed the SLM Acquisition Strategy template</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Made additional changes to the SLM IM</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Reviewed Geospatial Publication Investment Project documentation for Naomi</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Worked on making additional changes to the SLM handbook and framework diagram</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 1.5in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 1.5in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left: 1.5in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 1.5in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 1.5in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left: 1.5in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',	'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Completed the revised SLM draft IM and submitted to Mr. Lewis.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Completed making most of the changes to the Acquisition Strategy template recommended by IT Acquisitions.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;