(109,	13,	2,	1,	'2012-10-12',	'<p><span>Began working on the next ILM draft this week.&nbsp; Discovered that the concept of a ConOps as a deliverable artifact&nbsp;had been lost at some point in the various rewrites before my time.&nbsp; Received direction to add the concept from earlier drafts.&nbsp;&nbsp; The loss actually occurred when the basis changed from&nbsp;an ICE-based document to the current HHS-based version; HHS does not have ConOps, for some reason.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Also discovered a white paper with some very clear portfolio management language which will get added in; should&nbsp;finish the draft this week.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Continued familiarizing myself with assigned projects.&nbsp; Discovered an oddity in the CPIC site, with six minor projects showing identical budgets and expenditures.&nbsp; Following up with Tauqeer Aslam.</span></p>',	'<p>Short week with long meetings.</p>',	'<p><span>Two half day meetings on 570 reorganization and strategies moving forward toward developing a strategic plan for the division.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Nothing of consequence in the FDCCI weekly call; will meet next week to review the six final OR closing documents prior to final submission to OMB.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Had a good meeting with NOC representatives regarding roles/responsibilities under the ILM.&nbsp; This will be a weekly discussion for the near future, until we have reached some agreement on our separate roles.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 6pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></p>',	'<p>None</p>',	'<p>N/A</p>',	2,	4,	'2012-10-15 10:29:30',	4,	'2012-10-17 14:25:45'),
