(120,	2,	8,	1,	'2012-11-02',	'<p>Short week due to hurricane Sandy.</p>\r\n<p>AFMSS II - Worked on AFMSS II Project Charter background/purpose rewrite to be more in line with purpose of the charter document.</p>\r\n<p>AFMSS II APD - No activity</p>\r\n<p>NLSS - No activity.</p>\r\n<p>MDT - Validated the proper configuration for MDT Toughbook configurations to include the installation of SIM cards at time of purchase for all newly acquired devices.&nbsp; Worked on RFP issuance.&nbsp; Worked to answer law enforcement questions based on contract issuance delays.<span style=\"display: inline! important; float: none; word-spacing: 0px; font: small Tahoma; text-transform: none; color: #000000; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: #ffffff; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>',	'<p>MDT - Verified and ensured all orders for new MDT devices are configured with onboard SIM Cards and access to 4G networks as a minimum standard across the BLM Law Enforcement community.</p>',	'<p>MDT - Law enforcement updates.</p>',	'<p>MDT - Issuance of RFP.&nbsp; Too many delays on getting contract bids submitted and evaluated.</p>',	'<p>None at this time.</p>',	2,	1,	'2012-11-06 12:43:43',	2,	'2012-11-06 13:17:12'),
