(110,	53,	'Moneeka - You are required to take the Critical Thinking training (http://www.businesstrainingworks.com/Online-Critical-Thinking-Course.html); you will be provided the course login information via email. This is a comprehensive course and you will need to dedicate about seven (7) hours to take the course and associated test. You are authorized to utilize the middle office during this course.\r\n\r\nRobert/Ella - please make sure the phones are covered during this period; Moneeka will advise which day she will be taking the course. This is an all day course.',	NULL,	NULL,	2,	'2012-10-16 15:43:01'),
