(115,	56,	'You are required to put the resumes found in the Atechra Resumes folder into the proper format and house the converted resumes to the allocated location.',	NULL,	NULL,	2,	'2012-10-17 11:52:05'),
(116,	56,	'I do not understand.  Are you referring to all candidate resumes for PMP that we did not contact for an interview?\r\n',	NULL,	NULL,	11,	'2012-10-17 12:07:17'),
(117,	56,	'1.  Go to the Atechra Resumes folder under the CORPORATE FILES on this site.\r\n2.  Go to the IT Project Manager folder.\r\n3.  Go to the Atechra Format - Working folder.\r\n4.  You will find the resumes that need to be put in the Atechra Resume Folder.\r\n5.  Most of the resumes being put in the Atechra format may NOT be interviewed.\r\n6.  If the government believes the person is acceptable to be interview, the resume should be moved to the Interviewed Candidate Resumes folder.\r\n7.  If the government believes the person is unacceptable the resume should be move to the Hold For File folder.\r\n\r\nIt should be clear if the descriptions of the folders in the folder are read.',	NULL,	NULL,	2,	'2012-10-17 12:54:10'),
(118,	56,	'4. You will find the resumes that need to be put in the Atechra Resume FORMAT.',	NULL,	NULL,	2,	'2012-10-17 12:54:56'),
(119,	56,	'Lastly, this task has nothing to do with previously submitted resumes; ONLY RESUMES THAT EITHER ROBERT OR MYSELF place in the resumes to be put in the Atechra resume format folder.',	NULL,	NULL,	2,	'2012-10-17 12:59:47'),
(120,	55,	'I have place the updated list in my outbox.  The following task are required.\r\n(1)  Make sure the updated listing is placed under the corporate files section of this site in the appropriate folder.\r\n(2)  The highlighted corporations and contact person are to be mailed the Atechra brochure.  DO NOT PLACE the brochures in an envelope.',	NULL,	NULL,	2,	'2012-10-18 15:17:14'),
(121,	55,	'This task has been extended to Monday 10/22/2012.',	NULL,	NULL,	2,	'2012-10-19 08:10:05'),
